{
  "stem": "27509.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could see in his eyes that it meant all our arguments-- there is God, there is no God, or whatever it is-- didn't come into play for these three words that he heard from a teacher, spoken unprovoked and un-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] coming so freely.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that is just one aspect of the-- that comes to mind, now that we are looking into the-- into the memory lane.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course-- my mother-- my mother was a very presentable woman, as long as I remember her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She must have been-- I remember a picture of her, hanging on the wall of her brother, where my grandfather lived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very beautiful picture of a very lovely young woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She must have been 17, 18 at the time-- a really beautiful young woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had the misfortune of losing her mother very early.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was bought up by an uncle in Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she was an orphan, in terms of-- [INAUDIBLE], 17 or 18, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was born in a small township, [NON-ENGLISH], which is not far from Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in those little townships, there may not have been too much opportunity of earning a living or having three sufficient meals a day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was made up with a great deal of intellectual curiosity and learning, to fill the days and fill the inquisitiveness of mind.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in that little township, she learned-- she spoke fluent Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she told me that she used to get, [INAUDIBLE], Hebrew periodicals.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She didn't have much money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was obvious, the situation was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the Hebrew periodicals [INAUDIBLE] instead of buying yourself a bit of powder for her face, she bought a periodical instead.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
